00:08:07.150 --> 00:08:14.690
&gt;&gt; I was born in Algeria.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:24.850
My parents were elementary
school teachers from Syria

00:08:24.850 --> 00:08:27.850
who during the post-independence
period

00:08:27.850 --> 00:08:30.480
in Algeria taught
Arabic and Algeria.

00:08:30.480 --> 00:08:33.220
So, I was born there and
then we went back to Syria

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:35.960
and I was raised in
Syria, went to school there

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:38.680
and to medical school
in Damascus University,

00:08:38.680 --> 00:08:41.640
graduated from Damascus
University Medical School

00:08:41.640 --> 00:08:46.300
in 1988 and came right
after that to Chicago.

00:08:46.300 --> 00:08:49.700
I was first in class in
medical school and I remember

00:08:49.700 --> 00:08:53.050
that I gave the graduation
speech

00:08:53.050 --> 00:08:55.080
on behalf of the big class.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:58.570
We had about 550
people who graduated.

00:08:58.570 --> 00:09:02.660
And, among the graduates at that
time was someone whose name was

00:09:02.660 --> 00:09:06.390
Bashar al-Assad, who was the
son of the President of Syria

00:09:06.390 --> 00:09:08.290
at that time, Hafez al-Assad.

00:09:08.290 --> 00:09:12.350
Hafez al-Assad ruled Syria
for 30 years and at that time,

00:09:12.350 --> 00:09:15.610
Bashar was not being groomed
to be the next president.

00:09:15.610 --> 00:09:17.170
His older brother was, Bassel.

00:09:17.170 --> 00:09:21.820
Every Syrian dreams of the day
that they will go back and try

00:09:21.820 --> 00:09:24.570
to rebuild what has
been destroyed.

00:09:24.570 --> 00:09:28.450
Every Syrian American dreams of
the time that they can go back

00:09:28.450 --> 00:09:32.050
and walk peacefully in the
streets that they got to know

00:09:32.050 --> 00:09:36.740
and eat in the restaurants
that provide Syrian cuisine

00:09:36.740 --> 00:09:41.760
and listen to the
music of Syria.

00:09:41.760 --> 00:09:44.510
It looks like it's going to
be a long way from - from now.

00:09:44.510 --> 00:09:49.040
