cultural like practices,

00:12:41.290 --> 00:12:45.290
there's also differences
in like religious sect.

00:12:45.290 --> 00:12:50.180
What I've realized is I've grown
up as that kind of one culture

00:12:50.180 --> 00:12:52.230
and just religious sect kind

00:12:52.230 --> 00:12:55.100
of like was more
prominent in my life.

00:12:55.100 --> 00:12:57.570
So, definitely the
Palestinian culture

00:12:57.570 --> 00:13:04.060
and practices I've learned way
more about than Iranian culture

00:13:04.060 --> 00:13:05.360
or even Russian culture.

00:13:05.360 --> 00:13:06.660
That's probably what
I've learned the least

00:13:06.660 --> 00:13:07.960
about is Russian Culture.

00:13:07.960 --> 00:13:10.890
And, then I am [inaudible]
Muslim too.

00:13:10.890 --> 00:13:12.540
So, yeah, I've just
realized that.

00:13:12.540 --> 00:13:16.170
I didn't really have the
opportunity to learn as much

00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:18.640
as I would have liked to
about Iranian culture,

00:13:18.640 --> 00:13:20.560
Russian cultures, as
well as like Judaism

00:13:20.560 --> 00:13:22.360
and [inaudible] Islam too.

