00:55:29.690 --> 00:55:31.250
atheist, Muslims even.

00:55:31.250 --> 00:55:34.440
We have spotlighted
stories from people

00:55:34.440 --> 00:55:35.830
of all different backgrounds.

00:55:35.830 --> 00:55:38.610
Our platform is open and that's
why we encourage you to go

00:55:38.610 --> 00:55:41.200
on the site and I
wish there was a way

00:55:41.200 --> 00:55:46.780
where we actually could
showcase all 350 plus stories.

