00:56:07.550 --> 00:56:09.990
And, I think just even
listening to these stories

00:56:09.990 --> 00:56:12.640
and having these panelists
up here and listening

00:56:12.640 --> 00:56:15.250
to just different
perspectives shows you

00:56:15.250 --> 00:56:18.210
that we have actually
encompassed one

00:56:18.210 --> 00:56:20.890
