collections of narratives

00:56:20.890 --> 00:56:24.590
and stories and experiences and
we hope to continue to do more.

00:56:24.590 --> 00:56:27.560
You know, our goal is to
have thousands of stories.

00:56:27.560 --> 00:56:31.000
People from first generation
to fourth generation.

00:56:31.000 --> 00:56:34.190
And, we've done recordings
with StoryCorps in partnership

00:56:34.190 --> 00:56:36.080
with the Arab American
National Museum.

00:56:36.080 --> 00:56:39.130
