Minneapolis community.

00:56:39.130 --> 00:56:40.430
We do it in Chicago.

00:56:40.430 --> 00:56:41.730
We do it in New York.

00:56:41.730 --> 00:56:43.810
We've done it with the
university studies,

00:56:43.810 --> 00:56:45.790
exchange students
from the MENA region.

00:56:45.790 --> 00:56:49.920
So, like I said, it's - it's
- it's a very broad range

00:56:49.920 --> 00:56:52.230
of just people's
individual experiences.

00:56:52.230 --> 00:56:54.660
And, we never tell anybody
what to write or what to submit

00:56:54.660 --> 00:56:55.960
or what to talk about.

00:56:55.960 --> 00:56:57.450
They're free to do that.

00:56:57.450 --> 00:56:59.130
It's your story.

00:56:59.130 --> 00:57:01.970
You have autonomy over it and
you can share what you want.

00:57:05.050 --> 00:57:09.280
&gt;&gt; I feel a bit odd since it's
