00:57:09.280 --> 00:57:13.550
but I also had this reflection
that he raised that, you know,

00:57:13.550 --> 00:57:15.750
others considerable,
you know, geographic

00:57:15.750 --> 00:57:18.540
and ethnic diversities that's
really beautiful in chimes

00:57:18.540 --> 00:57:19.840
through these stories.

00:57:19.840 --> 00:57:23.400
It does seem like there's a
consistent story of immigration

00:57:23.400 --> 00:57:26.450
or - or having parents in
the context of immigration.

00:57:26.450 --> 00:57:27.750
And, so I was wondering

