00:57:50.570 --> 00:57:54.370
Again, we would love to
reach out to a broader range

00:57:54.370 --> 00:57:57.270
of people to, you know,
and different communities

00:57:57.270 --> 00:57:59.650
within the Muslim American
communities to, you know,

00:57:59.650 --> 00:58:02.400
come out and reach out to
