00:58:06.720 --> 00:58:09.670
of narratives, especially
diverse ones from people

00:58:09.670 --> 00:58:10.970
of all different backgrounds.

00:58:10.970 --> 00:58:12.570
So, we're very open to it.

00:58:12.570 --> 00:58:15.400
Again, you know, reach out
to us through the website.

00:58:15.400 --> 00:58:18.310
We're very active on social
media as well on Facebook,

00:58:18.310 --> 00:58:21.400
