about that a little bit in -

00:58:29.890 --> 00:58:31.600
in a little bit more
depth coming up.

00:58:31.600 --> 00:58:33.610
So, there are very,
very different ways

00:58:33.610 --> 00:58:36.660
where you can still get involved
and share your narrative

00:58:36.660 --> 00:58:39.830
with MALA or your -
your story in general.

00:58:39.830 --> 00:58:44.890
I hope that answered
the question.

00:58:48.840 --> 00:58:53.550
&gt;&gt; Okay, again, I have a
question from Ahmed and Supna

00:58:53.550 --> 00:58:58.900
