00:59:12.320 --> 00:59:17.080
Where you feel that the Muslim
community placed themselves

00:59:17.080 --> 00:59:19.360
and that is one question.

00:59:19.360 --> 00:59:24.290
And, the second question is,
do you think that the Muslims

00:59:24.290 --> 00:59:28.240
from Middle East and
