01:04:19.320 --> 01:04:21.600
and the communities, I'm
sure it comes with time

01:04:21.600 --> 01:04:23.420
as communities settle in.

01:04:23.420 --> 01:04:25.040
So, I'm not sure
about the Iowa one,

01:04:25.040 --> 01:04:26.340
