01:04:26.340 --> 01:04:28.280
[ Inaudible Response ]

01:04:28.280 --> 01:04:29.580
Sure.

01:04:29.580 --> 01:04:32.650
&gt;&gt; It's not just the Mosque -

01:04:32.650 --> 01:04:35.400
it's not just the
Mosque in Iowa.

01:04:35.400 --> 01:04:37.480
Muslims are part of
American folk culture,

01:04:37.480 --> 01:04:39.240
though people don't
recognize it.

