Benjamin Franklin when he did
his census of Philadelphia,

01:04:55.430 --> 01:04:57.300
he was - because
he was concerned

01:04:57.300 --> 01:04:59.240
that he felt Pennsylvania
was being taken

01:04:59.240 --> 01:05:02.000
over by Germans found
a Muslim community,

01:05:02.000 --> 01:05:04.140
significant Muslim
population in Philadelphia.

01:05:04.140 --> 01:05:07.830
That was in 1742, so.

01:05:07.830 --> 01:05:09.130
&gt;&gt; Interesting.

