with the radio -

01:12:03.290 --> 01:12:07.420
we have a radio station
partnership with WBEZ.

01:12:07.420 --> 01:12:10.370
And, a person from
WBEZ connected Shirley

01:12:10.370 --> 01:12:12.610
and her Chicago team
to Zainab and MALA.

01:12:12.610 --> 01:12:16.030
And, thus the partnership
was forged.

