interview recorded

01:12:24.920 --> 01:12:28.150
in partnership between
StoryCorps and MALA.

01:12:28.150 --> 01:12:31.080
And, sense then, there have
been 88 interviews recorded

01:12:31.080 --> 01:12:36.450
with over 90 participants
and more to be recorded.

01:12:36.450 --> 01:12:40.380
And, so this has been one of
the most successful partnerships

01:12:40.380 --> 01:12:41.740
to come out of the
Chicago booth.

01:12:41.740 --> 01:12:44.330
And, it's been a
really incredible ride.

01:12:44.330 --> 01:12:49.090
And, so I - I again, thank the
Chicago booth and the folks

01:12:49.090 --> 01:12:52.210
at MALA for starting
this partnership.

01:12:52.210 --> 01:12:56.780
Now, for those of you who've not
really perused the collection,

01:12:56.780 --> 01:12:59.730
if you haven't had an
opportunity to do so,

01:12:59.730 --> 01:13:03.290
