01:14:04.360 --> 01:14:09.980
But, there's Tunisia, Libya,
Saudi Arabia, India, London,

01:14:09.980 --> 01:14:14.250
Nigeria, Egypt, Lebanon,
and the list goes on.

01:14:14.250 --> 01:14:17.480
It's a really fantastic project

01:14:17.480 --> 01:14:20.560
that we are very
grateful to be a part of.

01:14:20.560 --> 01:14:24.290
And, again, emphasizing how
important partnerships are

01:14:24.290 --> 01:14:27.130
in order to get the word
out about StoryCorps,

01:14:27.130 --> 01:14:30.380
to have people understand that
their stories are important

01:14:30.380 --> 01:14:33.220
and whether you record
your story with StoryCorps

01:14:33.220 --> 01:14:36.260
or another organization or
on your own, it's important

01:14:36.260 --> 01:14:38.300
to capture these stories.

01:14:38.300 --> 01:14:41.610
It's important to make sure your
voice is heard and the stories

01:14:41.610 --> 01:14:44.890
of your community, whatever
type of community that may be,

01:14:44.890 --> 01:14:48.460
are archived and
saved in perpetuity.

